{"tid":1264960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家要堅持落去真香港人 唔好俾班垃圾政府挽返轉頭","createTime":"2019-06-29T03:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T03:05:40.000Z","uid":271154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"43f4a4bf15cda844545d7b7449db48c0a12a8608","tid":1264960,"uid":271154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:05:40.000Z","msg":"和理非同勇武派一定要繼續團結一致‼️‼️<br />\n<br />\n我地要堅持住我地啲訴求<br />\n<br />\n一定要放返嗰<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5</span>個人出黎<br />\n<br />\n要佢收返<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暴動</span>定性<br />\n<br />\n要班垃圾政府<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撒回惡法</span><br />\n<br />\n要佢地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">徹查612班狗嘅所作所為</span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以去到全軍覆沒<br />\n唔可以衰收尾<br />\n<br />\n我地輸唔起呢個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港</span><br />\n<br />\n好多<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共狗</span>都開晒ac <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千其唔可以俾佢地分化到</span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔好理佢地講咩 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">諗下俾人拉左入面嗰5個人</span>受緊嘅苦<br />\n受緊啲精神壓力<br />\n唔需要理啲同我地道不同不相為謀嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共狗</span><br />\n<br />\n班垃圾政府一直唔出黎就係想睇我地攰<br />\n睇我地開始覺得有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無力感</span>而放棄繼續抗議<br />\n所以我地要團結一致叫佢地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">收皮</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要撐住落去同呢個無賴政府繼續抗議</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持住呀<strong>真</strong>香港人</span>‼️‼️‼️"}]}